{"data":[{"date":"20:01 02/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 v\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i sau ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c 10 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u1ebd l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e2n binh v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 cao ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1eabn kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1edd c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u0129nh \u0111\u1ea1c, to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Do-Hung-Dung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i&nbsp;\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh 1 trong 3 su\u1ea5t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00e1c '\u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7' V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n&nbsp; Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. Khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kia \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng xem ra r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, c\u1ea3 L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n, L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long v\u00e0 Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i. Ch\u00ednh th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh khi c\u00e1c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh?</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-lai-tung-hoa-mu-de-tranh-su-theo-doi-cua-cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-168-192575.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hlv-park-hang-seo-lai-tung-hoa-mu-de-tranh-su-theo-doi-cua-cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-lai-tung-hoa-mu-de-tranh-su-theo-doi-cua-cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-168-192575.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i tung h\u1ecfa m\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tin d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0u \u00e1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. V\u00e0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn s\u1ebd trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi th\u00f3i quen s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c hay nh\u01b0 V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Th\u00e0nh Chung, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh hay V\u0103n Thanh... V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 'box-to-box' (ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng) ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 VN \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u1eafp s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, anh lu\u00f4n ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n. V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trieu Viet Hung\" title=\"Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/4-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-chien-thang-cua-hagl-truoc-slna.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i&nbsp;\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay. Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i HAGL do ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ecfi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a HAGL l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u0103n S\u01a1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, hay V\u0103n Thanh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 V\u0103n S\u01a1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y, b\u1ecf ng\u01b0\u1eddi kia l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo.&nbsp;\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 kh\u00e1c nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau, th\u1ebf n\u00ean nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111a n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1 th\u00fa v\u1ecb trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u1eeba qua c\u00f9ng th\u1ea7y Park. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110TQG l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\">HLV Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u00e1ng 2/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c KBS News \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5001","checkdouble":"192576"},{"date":"18:31 02/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cac-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, bao g\u1ed3m hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo b\u00e1o tin vui v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo b\u00e1o tin vui v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y Park cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c H\u1ed3ng Duy c\u00f3 tham d\u1ef1 Gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf U23 - C\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 v\u00e0 ASIAD hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo b\u00e1o c\u00e1o m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh b\u1ecb sung c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng tham gia bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng th\u00eam. Vi\u1ec7c H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o sau&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u1eabn Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y Park t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh v\u00e0 L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y song s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01a1n \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\">HLV Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br />\r\nV\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u00e1ng 2/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br />\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5000","checkdouble":"192577"},{"date":"05:39 03/08","title":"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-viet-nam-duoc-hua-thuong-tien-ty-cho-tam-hcv-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1edfng 1 t\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh HCV ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/U23-Viet-Nam-duoc-hua-thuong-tien-ty-cho-tam-HCV-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i luy\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u00e1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tin vui cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n HLV Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 hai nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0 Nh\u1ef1a Pha L\u00ea v\u00e0 Long Giang Land cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1edfng 1 t\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh HCV. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, d\u00f9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HCV ASIAD l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan, Nepal. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u1ea3 quan, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out, c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9, kinh nghi\u1ec7m m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD 2018, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8 t\u1edbi, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y (7/8), HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f9ng 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01a1n tu\u1ed5i sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.&nbsp;Hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c HCV ASIAD.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018-168-192566.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/18/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018-168-192566.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u1edd Reuters cho r\u1eb1ng L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c KBS News \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4999","checkdouble":"192593"},{"date":"06:11 03/08","title":"CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/clb-hagl-bat-ngo-vuon-len-dan-dau-tai-chau-a-ve-suc-hut.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean k\u00eanh Youtube.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/CLB-HAGL-bat-ngo-vuon-len-dan-dau-tai-chau-A-ve-suc-hut-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Depor&amp;Finanzas v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong th\u00e1ng 7 khi thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2,75 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube. Con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Buriram (ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 2,2 tri\u1ec7u).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HAGL &lsquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Vi\u1ec7c HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y NHM ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ng\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi trong th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1, ho\u00e0 1 v\u00e0 thua \u0111\u1ebfn 2&nbsp;tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;c\u1ea1nh tranh&rdquo; g\u1eaft gao v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a HAGL nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 10 l\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1,6 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem. X\u1ebfp tr\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Persib Bandung, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Indonesia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\">HLV HAGL tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4998","checkdouble":"192596"},{"date":"06:52 03/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8): Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine \u0111\u1ec1u tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 c\u1ef1 t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t quan tr\u1ecdng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, VFF ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Vinaphone \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eed l\u1eeda v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c trong m\u1eaft HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn NHM r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p U23 Palestine. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd\u00a0kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, 19h30 ng\u00e0y 038 Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, 19h30 ng\u00e0y 038 Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/4/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine,-19h30-ngay-038-Cho-mot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine:\u00a0Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 100% quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng NHM, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho ASIAD v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 AFF Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Do \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 nghi\u1ec7m n\u00ean c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01a1n tru khi th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ea1i g\u00ec bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 \u2018ch\u1ebft b\u1ecf\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0103n \u00fd, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1ea1c quan nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p U23 Palestine, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.\u00a0V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\">HLV Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u00e1ng 2/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>U23 Palestine \u2013 th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, U23 Palestine v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1, bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ea1 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 5-1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p U23 Qatar, d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 77 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine c\u00f3 m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi U23 Qatar, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a World Cup 2022 ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat 3-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, U23 Palestine s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng. T\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, HLV Sandouqa c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 mang theo nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a U23 Palestine sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 38) Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 38) Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine-(19h30-ngay-38)-Cho-con-mua-ban-thang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Palestine t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Abuaker, Fahkouri, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alashhab, Farawi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Abuwada, Fannoun, Dabbagh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Yousef, Qymbor\u2026, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 Termanini (CLB Eskilstuna) v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 El-Kayed (Prespa Birlik). V\u1edbi d\u00e0n tinh binh \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00ed do g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u1edf l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh ri\u00eang \u1edf k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tung nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-2 U23 Palestine</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n L\u00e2m; V\u0103n Thanh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Palestine: Fahkouri; Alashhab, Farawi, Qatmish, Termanini, Abuwada, Fannoun, El-Kayed, Dabbagh, Yousef, Qymbor.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft ...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng - C\u00fap Vinaphone 2018:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 3/8/2018:</strong></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h30:\u00a0Uzbekistan vs Oman\u00a0(Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">19h30: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Palestine (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 5/8/2018</strong></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h30: Uzbekistan vs Palestine\u00a0(Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV5, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<br>\r\n19h30: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Oman\u00a0(Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV5, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 7/8/2018</strong></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h30: Oman vs Palestine (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<br>\r\n19h30: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4997","checkdouble":"192600"},{"date":"22:00 02/08","title":"Bayern Munich m\u1ec9a mai Juventus ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec \u201c\u00f4ng gi\u00e0\u201d Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u00f4ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c Juventus b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang \u1edf Bernabeu nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich m\u1ec9a mai Juventus mua Cristiano Ronaldo cho ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern Munich m\u1ec9a mai Juventus mua Cristiano Ronaldo cho ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mua Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u1ea5y v\u1eady m\u00e0 Juventus v\u1eabn ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u1eafn r\u0103ng duy\u1ec7t chi \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00ec anh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quan \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge: \u201cCristiano Ronaldo sao? T\u00f4i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Andrea Agnelli quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh theo \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh tay nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u00ean g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 Juventus, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y h\u1ee3p l\u00fd b\u1edfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Bayern Munich ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eeba ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 phung ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi n\u00f3 \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e2u n\u0103m c\u1ee7a CLB.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu IC Cup 2018 v\u00e0 run r\u1ee7i thay, si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 5/8 \u1edf M\u1ef9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-thu-loi-tu-cristiano-ronaldo-khong-nhieu-nhu-nguoi-ta-van-nghi-176-192158.html\">Juventus thu l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo: C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4996","checkdouble":"192582"},{"date":"20:27 02/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 2/8: Juventus v\u00e0 Milan ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-28-juventus-va-milan-hoan-tat-thuong-vu-hoan-doi-ngoi-sao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mua Bonucci, Milan m\u01b0\u1ee3n Higuain</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 28 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 28 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Diem-tin-bongda24hvn-toi-ngay-28---Tin-bong-da-24h-moi-nhat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Leonardo Bonucci</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Juventus \u0111\u00f3n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m xa c\u00e1ch, trong khi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Mattia Caldara ra \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh thu\u00ea \u1edf Atalanta. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain c\u0169ng chia tay th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 37 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/202312-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gonzalo Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 28 Juventus v\u00e0 Milan ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 28 Juventus v\u00e0 Milan ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-28-Juventus-va-Milan-hoan-tat-thuong-vu-hoan-doi-ngoi-sao-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yerry Mina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Harry Maguire v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Leicester City, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t Yerry Mina d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i khi anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barcelona. Th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh cao to \u0111\u1ebfn 1m94 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi ba b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Colombia, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao MU n\u00e0o s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ra \u0111i theo h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" title=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Marcos Rojo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina \u1edf Old Trafford, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Marcos Rojo v\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng cho anh l\u00e0 Everton, CLB n\u1eeda xanh v\u00f9ng Merseyside t\u0103m tia trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau khi ch\u1ecbu thua Man Utd \u1edf ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mina. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, Matteo Darmian c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u00dd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus ho\u1eb7c Inter Milan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sap co Jack Grealish\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/nho-john-terry-chelsea-sap-co-jack-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jack Grealish</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng Jack Grealish thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh t\u1eeb \u00edt n\u0103m qua v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Aston Villa. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd g\u1ecdi t\u00ean Chelsea nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng Man Utd, Liverpool v\u00e0 Totttenham. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 b\u1edfi c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry, ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Grealish v\u00e0 h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e0n em gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Mignolet\" title=\"thu mon Mignolet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/barca-la-ben-do-hoan-hao-cua-mignolet.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Simon Mignolet</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Barcelona b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u0103m tia \u201cth\u1ea3m h\u1ecda\u201d Simon Mignolet c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Jasper Cillesen quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i khi kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u00e3i m\u00e0i \u0111\u0169ng qu\u1ea7n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Kasper Schmeichel, Jordan Pickford hay Jack Butland, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Thibaut Courtois v\u1ec1 tay Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4995","checkdouble":"192578"},{"date":"21:25 02/08","title":"Atletico Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/28/atletico-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-gay-soc-voi-batshuayi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Michy Batshuayi t\u1eeb Chelsea, theo L'Equipe, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giroud t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Atletico Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/giroud-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-o-chelsea-172-192310.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Giroud </span>c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Michy Batshuayi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Michy Batshuayi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/Atletico-Madrid-muon-mua-Michy-Batshuayi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giroud t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Atletico Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain, song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiroud ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e2u n\u0103m \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Batshuayi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Michy Batshuayi t\u1eeb Chelsea, theo L'Equipe, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Newcastle phong ngu ngay tho truoc Chelsea cua Batshuayi\" title=\"Newcastle phong ngu ngay tho truoc Chelsea cua Batshuayi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/29/tiet-lo-tuong-lai-batshuayi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Atletico chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Batshuayi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf Chelsea, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9\u00a03 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng sau Morata v\u00e0 Giroud. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Tammy Abraham c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Batshuayi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Batshuayi mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu Atletico ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Atletico d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993. Ngo\u00e0i Atletico th\u00ec Valencia c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, song \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4994","checkdouble":"192579"},{"date":"21:41 02/08","title":"Barca nh\u1eafm Arturo Vidal n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/12/barca-nham-arturo-vidal-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi. Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Barca-muon-mua-Arturo-Vidal-voi-gia-30-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Rabiot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPSG kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gia h\u1ea1n. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-nhan-don-dau-vu-rabiot-180-192514.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rabiot s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 490.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rabiot, Barca \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal hay Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, song nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Ramsey x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Arsenal, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Nzonzi mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Unai Emery \u1edf Emirates h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Arturo Vidal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Vidal\" title=\"tien ve Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/bayern-munich-bo-ngo-kha-nang-ban-sao-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u sao Juventus ra \u0111i\u00a0n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Vidal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 30 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Bayern y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou tin r\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Vidal s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec Inter Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Barca c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou, Vidal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4993","checkdouble":"192580"},{"date":"23:04 02/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Barcelona tham v\u1ecdng qua m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3 Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/thu-mon-barcelona-tham-vong-qua-mat-ca-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Marc-Andre ter Stegen c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n cho t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan sau khi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ee9c danh th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u01b0u ti\u00ean th\u00e2m ni\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB, tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Lionel Messi nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00ean h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Barcelona.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca sau khi Iniesta ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca sau khi Iniesta ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/thu-mon-barcelona-tham-vong-qua-mat-ca-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ngay c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a g\u1eafn b\u00f3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u01b0 Marc-Andre ter Stegen c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 t\u00e2n th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh cho CLB. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTo\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea7u ra \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong Barca c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh v\u00e0 n\u00eau l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Barcelona s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p AC Milan v\u00e0 Boca Juniors tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Alaves \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u khai m\u1ea1c La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4992","checkdouble":"192583"},{"date":"06:26 03/08","title":"Kh\u00f4ng mua ai thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, t\u00e2n HLV Real Madrid tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi X\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c k\u1ebf th\u1eeba v\u00e0 c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0n anh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Zinedine Zidane c\u0169ng v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a Gareth Bale gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn n\u00e0o tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Bernabeu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui tin Bale thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo \u1edf Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui tin Bale thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo \u1edf Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/HLV-Lopetegui-tin-Bale-thay-the-Ronaldo-o-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui tin Bale thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0 nh\u01b0 l\u00fac ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ngay sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n hai th\u00e1ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi X\u1ee9 Wales v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man Utd ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Tottenham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Gareth Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c k\u1ebf th\u1eeba v\u00e0 c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0n anh Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cKhi t\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Cristiano v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1edbm b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ea5t \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Cristiano ra sao, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Los Blancos. K\u1ebf th\u1eeba di s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y sao cho x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Gareth Bale s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-180-192564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-180-192564.html\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid: Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4991","checkdouble":"192589"},{"date":"05:54 03/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u201cch\u00ea\u201d Thibaut Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/nong-hlv-real-bat-ngo-che-thibaut-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u00e2n HLV Real, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas, qua \u0111\u00f3 xua tan nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois.</h2><h2>HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd &ldquo;ch\u00ea&rdquo; Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u00ea Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u00ea Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Nong-HLV-Real-bat-ngo-che-Thibaut-Courtois-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua Thibaut Courtois&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Keylor Navas \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 31, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 Real \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Thibaut Courtois nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf cho Navas.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a Los Blancos l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 d\u1eedng d\u01b0ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Real. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Navas v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Navas r\u1ea5t t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft v\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui cho th\u1ea5y Real Madrid \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Thibaut Courtois. H\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 l\u00ean Chelsea b\u1edfi l\u1ebd th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Blues. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi&nbsp;Courtois trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Courtois, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng Thibaut Courtois \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 sang n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4990","checkdouble":"192594"},{"date":"05:57 03/08","title":"Sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0n anh t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc ng\u1ee3i khen","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/sao-moi-noi-cua-chelsea-duoc-dan-anh-tam-tac-ngoi-khen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 18 tu\u1ed5i Callum Hudson-Odoi m\u1edbi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu Arsenal vs Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng khi \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/chelsea-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-icc-2018-dem-nay-372-192499.html\" target=\"_blank\">nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</span>. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Antonio Rudiger \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 FA Cup.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Azpilicueta khen ng\u1ee3i Hudson-Odoi sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Azpilicueta khen ng\u1ee3i Hudson-Odoi sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/sao-moi-noi-cua-chelsea-duoc-dan-anh-tam-tac-ngoi-khen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Azpilicueta khen ng\u1ee3i Hudson-Odoi sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Maurizio Sarri c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. M\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Callum Hudson-Odoi. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 18 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 Cesar Azpilicueta khen ng\u1ee3i Hudson-Odoi h\u1ebft l\u1eddi: \u201cCallum c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, v\u1eady m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCallum ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c Chelsea trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, trong khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 18 n\u00e0y th\u00ec hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean Callum v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1eefa, v\u1eady m\u00e0 h\u00e3y coi xem c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ra sao cho Bellerin. Quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span><br>\r\nG\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, Arsenal k\u1ebft th\u00fac chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4989","checkdouble":"192584"}]}